id: zw_cc_user_credential_nvm
label: User Credential Command Class - NVM
category: Z-Wave|Command Classes
description: >
  Enables storage of User Credential Commnad Class in the NVM (non-volatile memory).
  This component implements NVM handling APIs for SiliconLabs hardware for User Credential Command Class.
  The number of Users and Credentials are limited because of flash size and can be overridden.
package: Z-Wave
quality: production
